reviewText: I'm reviewing this although we purchased for a gift.  My daughters are the proud owners of EVERY BARBIE DVD that we know exists.  They're wonderfully made - they are fun to watch, the characters are beautiful - and it's in the sense that there is always a positive message and they promote good.  The fairy movies are great - these are three different fairy movies, so you really get an assortment.The songs are always beautiful and catchy - yes, I know the majority of the little songs and I sing them with my girls.  All three of these are excellent movies.
summary: Every girl needs every Barbie movie.
